@startuml evolution_fitness
skinparam monochrome true
left to right direction

title Ciclo di valutazione fitness

node "Persistence" as P <<Cloud/Hub - Linux Server>>
database "MQTT Broker" as MQTT <<Edge Node - Linux Gateway>>
node "Core Runtime" as CR <<Distributed Node - RPi / ESP32 / STM32>>
component "Agent FSM" as FSM <<Distributed Node - RPi / ESP32 / STM32>>
node "Fitness Evaluator" as FE <<Cloud/Hub - Linux Server>>

P -right-> MQTT : [1] publish OHLCV\n"tr4d3rz/data/ohlcv/{symbol}"
MQTT -right-> CR : [2] deliver market tick
CR -right-> FSM : [3] process OHLCV through FSM
FSM -down-> CR : [4] Prediction(direction, confidence)
CR -right-> FE : [5] submit prediction + next_tick
FE -left-> FE : [6] compare prediction\nwith realized tick
FE -left-> MQTT : [7] publish fitness update\n"tr4d3rz/ecosystem/fitness/{agent_id}"

note bottom of P
  **Hosted on:** Cloud/Hub - Linux Server
  **Topic:** tr4d3rz/data/ohlcv/{symbol}
  **Payload (CBOR map):**
  {
    "v": 1,
    "ts": uint64,
    "node": node_id,
    "type": "data.ohlcv",
    "symbol": text,
    "open": float64,
    "high": float64,
    "low": float64,
    "close": float64,
    "volume": uint64
  }
end note

note bottom of FE
  **Hosted on:** Cloud/Hub - Linux Server
  **Topic:** tr4d3rz/ecosystem/fitness/{agent_id}
  **Payload (CBOR map):**
  {
    "v": 1,
    "ts": uint64,
    "node": node_id,
    "type": "ecosystem.fitness.update",
    "agent_id": UUID,
    "fitness_score": float32,
    "symbols_count": uint32,
    "timestamp": uint64
  }
end note

footer Hosting: Cloud/Hub Linux Server -> Persistence/Fitness Evaluator; Edge Linux Gateway -> MQTT Broker; Distributed RPi/ESP32/STM32 -> Core Runtime/Agent FSM | MQTT Topics: tr4d3rz/data/ohlcv/{symbol}, tr4d3rz/ecosystem/fitness/{agent_id} | CBOR Payloads: OHLCV market tick; agent_id, fitness_score, symbols_count, timestamp
@enduml
